<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
	<head>
		<title>C.I.S Tours</title>
		<link rel="icon" href="/icons/favicon.ico">
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Roboto" rel="stylesheet"> 
		<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/icon?family=Material+Icons" rel="stylesheet">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/style.css" type="text/css">
		<link rel="stylesheet" href="/stylesheets/terms.css" type="text/css">
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.2.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
		<script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jqueryui/1.12.1/jquery-ui.min.js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
		<nav>
			<% include nav %>
		</nav>
		<main>
			<div class="parallax" style="background-image: url('')"></div>
			<div id="cont">
				<div id="terms">
					<div>Terms and conditions</div>
					<div id="privacy">
						<p>Privacy policy</p>
						<p>When you book a tour we ask you some personal information as first name, last name, e-mail address and phone number. We will use these information just to contact you in relation to the tour you ar booking. No spam will be sent to your contact information.</p>
					</div>
					<div id="refund">
						<p>Refund Policy</p>
						<p>If you want to delete the tour you booked and you want your money back, you can ask for a refund following the link that is sent along with the ticket. You can ask for a refund up to 14 days to the tour date.</p>
					</div>
					<div id="payment">
						<p>Payment security</p>
						<p>We don't store any of your credit card information, as we use the BrainTree SDK to get payments.</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
			<footer>
				<% include footer %>
			</footer>
		</main>
	</body>
</html>
